'''東部安那托利亞地區'''（{{lang-tr|Doğu Anadolu Bölgesi}}）是[[土耳其|土耳其]]的七個[[土耳其地理分區|地理分區]]之一，位於該國的東側。該地區多數位於[[亞美尼亞高原|亞美尼亞高原]]<ref>{{Cite book|author=Lynch, H.F.B.|title=Armenia, Travels and Studies|publisher=London|year=1901|volume=2|pages=391|quote=The natural boundary between Armenia and Asia Minor is the course of the Western Euphrates between the town of Kemah, and its passage through Taurus below Keban-Maden.|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|author=Oswald, Felix|title=A Treatise on the Geology of Armenia|publisher=London|year=1906|language=en}}</ref>，有著七個分區中最高的平均海拔，也是七分區中最大的地理分區，面積達146,330平方-{zh-hans:千米;zh-hant:千米;zh-tw:公里;}-，但是人口密度為七分區之末，2014年該地區有5,906,565的人口。該地區原本被稱為[[西亞美尼亞|西亞美尼亞]]，但在[[亞美尼亞種族大屠殺|亞美尼亞種族大屠殺]]發生後，變被換為現今的名稱<ref name="Sahakyan">{{cite book|last=Sahakyan|first=Lusine|title=Turkification of the Toponyms in the Ottoman Empire and the Republic of Turkey|year=2010|publisher=Arod Books|location=Montreal|isbn=978-0969987970|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Hovannisian|first1=Richard|title=The Armenian genocide cultural and ethical legacies|date=2007|publisher=Transaction Publishers|location=New Brunswick, N.J.|isbn=1412835925|page=3|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=K3monyE4CVQC|language=en|access-date=2016-01-05|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010030024/https://books.google.com/books?id=K3monyE4CVQC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

